text: "It's Only Over for You" is a 1985 song by Tammy Wynette for her 26th studio album Sometimes When We Touch. In 1987 Tanya Tucker's version was released as a single and is the fourth single from her 15th studio album Girls Like Me. It went to number 12 on the Canadian RPM Country Tracks charts and number 8 on the Billboard Hot Country charts. ==References== Category:1985 songs Category:Country songs Category:Tammy Wynette songs Category:Tanya Tucker songs
